{"title":"Esofagitis","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología/Esofagitis-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Esofagitis","guid":"aJTpCztw5WCggz-lW_X1FQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Manifestaciones clínicas del ERGE\\N(Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease)","guid":"MdUTSc6UPiFHj2mUKLZnyg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Síntomas clásicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Pirosis (Heartburn):","guid":"4FgQ0fiYL14xzF3vz6axqg","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Sensación de ardor en el área retroesternal, postprandial [2].","guid":"lO2LcdE0A1Bhdc_T8nIjgg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"• Problemática si ocurre ≥2 días/semana [2].","guid":"oZmTnWk2HZU1cy2poWqIzQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"• Regurgitación:","guid":"-ZaGquKMN6Bz8zYuIqHx4A","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Percepción del flujo de contenido gástrico hacia la boca o hipofaringe [2].","guid":"VK810ZBA4nMz2m_RiFQiJQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Material ácido mezclado con alimentos no digeridos.","guid":"7g2vieZrw-5d0M3Gyq2tMw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"2. Síntomas adicionales:","guid":"HLwlo0ciXBL2ePShr-n29Q","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Disfagia:","guid":"ZgW20yPV9z9aNQIAOB-8KA","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Común en pirosis crónica, puede indicar esofagitis por reflujo o estenosis esofágica [6].","guid":"09fQZF-Go8IrFmdrBSoFQw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"• Dolor torácico:","guid":"VzmoMcI_hnKtkNpscBYb6A","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Puede imitar angina pectoris, descrito como opresivo o ardor,\\Nsubesternal, radiando a espalda, cuello, mandíbula, brazos [1].","guid":"FAlL5v_vRxw22NUm8bjYYA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Duración: minutos a horas; resuelve espontáneamente o con antiácidos.","guid":"ircCDGpZPiH6zOOt17pVNg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"• Relacionado con comidas, despierta a pacientes, exacerbado por estrés emocional.","guid":"suCPajIEOsdByVIdVdbXaA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"• Pirosis es un predictor pobre de ERGE en dolor torácico (monitorización de pH esofágico) [7].","guid":"rh-El3tzyQA8evGcepoCtg","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"9","text":"• Hipersalivación (Water brash):","guid":"_X4yZJbC2H8eUmx2-OhCyw","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Secreción de hasta 10 mL de saliva/minuto en respuesta al reflujo.","guid":"EvLijs2syvpYGw83rR1Ccg","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"9","text":"• Sensación de globo:","guid":"2Bu33zaqbDtmx-SOYJeYPw","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Percepción constante de bulto en la garganta, posible relación con ERGE [8].","guid":"XVxYSqs63unm8VC5GzE9ZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"9","text":"• Náuseas:","guid":"J_4yXx7F8vnOHouoKoncsg","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Infrecuente, considerar ERGE en náuseas inexplicables [9].","guid":"Ap15NOOWCysgFehA6ADtdQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Hallazgos\\Nradiográficos en\\NERGE","guid":"PwRfSDtSdMx-5FDCgrAgxg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"1. Utilidad del examen de deglución\\Ncon bario de doble contraste:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• Limitado diagnóstico en ERGE:","guid":"RO2er9s8QSVMAf6M5eQHvA","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Reflujo de bario: Significado dudoso (25-71% en sintomáticos; 20% en controles normales) [10].","guid":"UDWh6iPyi0S6TjZDSrUpdw","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"• Precisión\\Ndiagnóstica:","guid":"l42hRgnplJB_YMWeoLZaXw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Esofagitis leve: 25%.","guid":"EUI1-6gnwjXxVuzwDgApWw","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• Esofagitis moderada: 82%.","guid":"zawRAvi_-f7be9fphAMUGw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"• Esofagitis severa: 99% [11].","guid":"bshv9rqa66_N58mhgtJC3A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"23","text":"2. Cambios mucosos asociados con\\Nesofagitis y estenosis pépticas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Esofagitis por reflujo temprana:","guid":"hvzXJWGE0un5MaA7yZOxUA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Mucosa del tercio distal del esófago granular/nodular, con lucencias mal definidas de 1-3 mm [12].","guid":"ryfNE95BFj9z7gW1f-uAQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"• Esofagitis erosiva:","guid":"7qpKjJaXstlArK88ygGjgw","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Úlceras superficiales y erosiones visibles como pequeñas acumulaciones de bario cerca\\Nde la unión gastroesofágica, rodeadas por halo radiolúcido de mucosa edematosa.","guid":"uMDjRd6g4aYQZPgJpPiJhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"• Estenosis\\Npéptica benigna:","guid":"9MeDukBi55yy-rXzZJs_ZA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Área de estrechamiento concéntrico y liso en el esófago distal\\N(1-4 cm de longitud; 0. 2-2.0 cm de diámetro).","guid":"j3uk7bLC2_jKS3b_TBM-wA","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"31","text":"• Estenosis asimétrica: Pared con cicatriz excéntrica.","guid":"mkXumI19lUIyNqFN9RJeMA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones\\Ndel ERGE","guid":"64iUY91L0eDnZaMBYHVgpw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"1. Esófago de Barrett.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"2. Estenosis esofágica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"3. Adenocarcinoma esofágico.","guid":"JkuyRi8OOMQK3L7QVQBRLg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"4. Complicaciones\\Nextraesofágicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Laringitis crónica.","guid":"lYIBIXte29YFWXeI8PGO2g","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"• Exacerbación de asma.","guid":"iXM5q67pSxjFsJL496Pskw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de ERGE (Enfermedad\\Npor Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"mCsOqXTyYyou0hu2AJ012A","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"1. Pacientes con\\Nsíntomas clásicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Pirosis y/o regurgitación:","guid":"TBPPLn-g4efeCxCCdmGdXw","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Dx basado en síntomas clínicos [2, 13].","guid":"gBcYH_hHD2VwhnW5uh5-qA","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Evaluación adicional\\Nsi presentan:","guid":"u9Cpp61AOqlQCHix-BH4MQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Signos de alarma.","guid":"DAO63O4wsfXm-GY6edc0kw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Factores de riesgo para esófago de Barrett.","guid":"maeqn-MPil0bODgllK2bBw","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"• Imágenes GI anormales.","guid":"TEhwXNiP6q909jJ0p_nokA","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"• Respuesta\\Na IBPs:","guid":"N-oagqLa9X8NHatAlg2Rrw","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• 40-90% de pacientes con respuesta sintomática a IBPs.","guid":"0LdzcWRabSrf0mel55zhTQ","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• No criterio dx para ERGE [14,15].","guid":"NA4Tj5yivCoZL637PIcoww","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"• Meta-análisis: Sensibilidad 78%, especificidad 54%.","guid":"tohPZ9ySpJWBrmXO-ISuhA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"• No correlación con medidas objetivas (monitorización de pH ambulatorio) [15].","guid":"Ihw8zIDQRJvBYYvi6A7_jg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"46","text":"2. Pacientes sin\\Nsíntomas clásicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Otros síntomas:","guid":"9j-eclZTsc2XphwlsNTk2A","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Dolor torácico, sensación de globo, tos crónica, ronquera, sibilancias, náuseas.","guid":"Wu0xyJLceqOewr-QTMXzLw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• No suficientes para dx clínico de ERGE sin pirosis/regurgitación.","guid":"40M9HtTJ0SlR3Eg6SoXRiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"59","text":"• Excluir otros trastornos antes de\\Natribuir síntomas a ERGE:","guid":"D5HosRHAsds2xhBNZM9vYA","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Ej: Dolor torácico inexplicado → ECG y\\Nprueba de esfuerzo antes de evaluación GI.","guid":"26Be91L4a_oYf-o8oUuu3Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación en pacientes seleccionados con ERGE\\N(Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"hODYM399fVl7y9bMD9P_1A","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Evaluación\\Nadicional:","guid":"BuJLp2dJwngcIm7hT9BSOA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Requerida en pacientes con\\Nsospecha de ERGE para:","guid":"AetgsHgvqAlxQaS7egF-7A","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Descartar etiologías alternativas.","guid":"PPdGbz3WXvdQ8AV16_5DIA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Confirmar el dx de ERGE.","guid":"fq_SZ2618iIYwxRMavCtXg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"• Evaluar complicaciones","guid":"u7MtEHuvjol0SqCUh6XWdg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"65","text":"Endoscopia\\Ngastrointestinal alta:","guid":"FJkMBsWRdw18LRzxhSWMEg","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Evaluar signos de alarma o imágenes anormales (si no se realizó en los últimos 3 meses).","guid":"BtL1L4blYkJuv15vNuF2JQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"• Cribado de esófago de Barrett en pacientes con factores de riesgo.","guid":"GwiyJ-3TvN2p5nQuzob4pw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"• Biopsias dirigidas a áreas de metaplasia, displasia o mucosa normal en ausencia de anomalías visibles\\N(para evaluar esofagitis eosinofílica) [16].","guid":"WfIcNI-MO-O8A_xQtFD8Yw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"• No necesaria para dx de ERGE.","guid":"obe_vFkAbLpG_Qcnlszlcw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"• Detecta manifestaciones esofágicas de ERGE\\N(ej. Metaplasia de Barrett, esofagitis erosiva).","guid":"wpB_9mT-rY5jDuEFc-is-Q","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"• Descartar malignidad del tracto GI superior.","guid":"qBWoT7gd5uwZSjfgD4Q3XQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"72","text":"• Descartar otras etiologías en síntomas refractarios a IBPs.","guid":"q2K8XLNxkHsB0YVMRk-8BQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"71","text":"Características\\Nde alarma:","guid":"baf42qZyETiI2mFGgVayiw","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Sugieren\\Nmalignidad GI:","guid":"axEVlyi1jOxNwC1q-KFGOA","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Dispepsia de inicio reciente en ≥60 años.","guid":"IN0t9BAmH6sL17zf8W3BoA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"• Sangrado GI (hematemesis, melena, hematoquecia, sangre oculta en heces).","guid":"8onVESbiCDth0kvFw0WGrg","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"• Anemia por deficiencia de hierro.","guid":"5njyb-3Z3Nwt_fxsadcrDg","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"• Anorexia.","guid":"yRhFiA1BgHZ8jdNIx5fjtw","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"• Pérdida de peso inexplicada.","guid":"Uefr09w5RR3KlGh6wcyUrw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"81","text":"• Disfagia.","guid":"EhbQHOe1IvO4jx-JmUUOBA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"81","text":"• Odinofagia.","guid":"xCoothnfKrDTl6U-4ReGdQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"81","text":"• Vómitos persistentes.","guid":"9vm9PfGt5u1tpGubJMSQXw","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"81","text":"• Cáncer GI en un pariente de primer grado.","guid":"6fHLUFRX4SFe_ruQoY9nsg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"65","text":"Factores de riesgo para\\Nesófago de Barrett:","guid":"QzcmPiTRy0Xm6wAc90agpw","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Cribado recomendado para pacientes con múltiples factores de riesgo\\N(uno debe ser duración de ERGE ≥5-10 años).","guid":"420M_CYbfItpm70hSv9bBw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Factores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"zohIU7J8Kddfs1c2za7kbQ","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• Duración de ERGE ≥5-10 años.","guid":"rd7wgHfvsoIbhYOB9km-0Q","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"• Edad ≥50 años.","guid":"E11DlBrExqM3NSKVisWluQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"• Sexo masculino.","guid":"yxPhofH2qSZxEE1jL7jpdg","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"• Raza blanca.","guid":"-muFGosyKE2Sj-Q96PcPEg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"93","text":"• Hernia hiatal.","guid":"l2j11Utj1WkYmX049PtDYw","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"93","text":"• Obesidad.","guid":"WnAbWIkaS-8LpP7zx0JDaA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"93","text":"• Reflujo nocturno.","guid":"qwCzyooeoJmd0__1DDNiAQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"93","text":"• Uso de tabaco (pasado o presente).","guid":"Ibytk1zNOsfbYzrZY3ij8g","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"93","text":"• Pariente de primer grado con esófago de Barrett y/o adenocarcinoma.","guid":"Eg6Xar6QiXU6O14_qKDFfw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"65","text":"Imágenes anormales del tracto\\Ngastrointestinal superior:","guid":"ddfE2oM83FCs5EYIJ2H7pw","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Imágenes abdominales no requeridas para dx de ERGE pero pueden ser realizadas para evaluar síntomas concurrentes.","guid":"3STC3gWcFm70h9V5P7-Hsw","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"• Anomalías luminales en imágenes GI superiores pueden justificar evaluación diagnóstica con endoscopia GI alta.","guid":"BkdaPmUISoIYQfxQGWPXbQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"0","text":"Hallazgos endoscópicos en ERGE\\N(Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"j9FQmIyL8D-JQ-Hcb6iZmQ","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"1. Endoscopia\\Ngastrointestinal alta:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"• Pacientes\\Ncon ERGE:","guid":"JWFul1x9abfYi0ExMkOUeA","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Puede ser normal o mostrar esofagitis de diversos grados [17].","guid":"zdwzPjuMZxEj8cJ1kGj6lA","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• ~30% de pacientes no tratados presentan esofagitis endoscópica.","guid":"G2BkQtJt2dtsf0iRicuV0Q","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• Severidad y duración de síntomas ≠ severidad de esofagitis.","guid":"kmEOnyd4KliRC8YLjTERig","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"107","text":"• Esofagitis péptica:","guid":"EIQQhgk07qtfQcyV15xe5A","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"• Ulceraciones: Forma irregular/lineal, múltiples, en esófago distal.","guid":"5iJWUhm6xlUQsvrK9mdsZg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"• Comparación: Esofagitis infecciosa/inducida por medicamentos → Ulceraciones en esófago medio.","guid":"d3sRI8LlLPT4P4_2-cr7BA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"106","text":"2. Hallazgos endoscópicos\\Nen ERGE prolongado:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Estenosis péptica.","guid":"JPGKO9BeLSjMhboQjDncPg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Metaplasia de Barrett.","guid":"slKzoKj8Lrw-Ldje_DN9lg","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"• Adenocarcinoma esofágico.","guid":"nV0rHOQHSmsjlHs-_tfmrQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"106","text":"3. Grado de severidad\\Nde esofagitis:","guid":"Efjg9ra1jl44-435fStIlw","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"• Esofagitis\\Nerosiva:","guid":"Bqjr6cYGoG-XESRN6RXvCA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"• Grado según severidad para guiar el manejo.","guid":"CWbWCEd01SOd1mru48RGNA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"• Clasificaciones endoscópicas para disminuir la variabilidad entre operadores.","guid":"R9y-ZyWJm6tDR7F5KjYElQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"• Clasificación de Los Ángeles: Más evaluada y utilizada para esofagitis [18].","guid":"u0mh9osuIO8xn4E7ZlYW_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"• Clasificación de\\NLos Ángeles:","guid":"oBcpl2mBcu7Q-IDjYl_xvA","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"General","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Evalúa severidad por extensión de anormalidad mucosa.","guid":"OlSlx9AvOZaLmZkFieqGLQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Complicaciones registradas por separado.","guid":"NIVcZLOyro2bkXYUr4oUQw","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"• Ruptura mucosa: Área de desprendimiento adyacente a mucosa normal en epitelio escamoso, con/sin exudado.","guid":"u440ifzSWQRbjV7LucM_3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"124","text":"• Grado A: Una o más rupturas mucosas, cada una ≤5 mm de longitud","guid":"eg0sNME2502e46fpq9WkMw","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"124","text":"• Grado B: Al menos una ruptura mucosa >5 mm, no continua entre los pliegues mucosos adyacentes","guid":"LE-UxlSnWGIyU19XriCWGg","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"124","text":"• Grado C: Al menos una ruptura mucosa continua entre los pliegues mucosos adyacentes, no circunferencial","guid":"bo9FRAMAkBYryCq2nyXBhQ","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"124","text":"• Grado D: Ruptura mucosa que involucra al menos tres cuartas partes de la circunferencia luminal","guid":"ScLXdYCHbPdCHhBXnhk2Lg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial del ERGE\\N(Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"NbePqPmTxILON4hqIU9-kA","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"1. Esófagitis\\Ninfecciosa:","guid":"rH4H3-LDfuxzhSdSL2_vNg","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Causas: Infección.","guid":"mGjZtKMKnB11A0h9rp3FKA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"p0n6A5RTbCUCsF9PAw3Rqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"2. Esofagitis\\Npor pastillas:","guid":"PeChhcnsp24KCa_-HbWslQ","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"• Causas: Medicamentos.","guid":"yVpTIjspCurVAbQks7j8PA","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"n5owoCpr2IqTutRcUrqgEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"3. Esofagitis\\Neosinofílica:","guid":"_Hq6WL1cevm_vaXS-p_FAA","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Causas: Inflamación eosinofílica.","guid":"pIE1zjmp0VsRDAeaggi4Fg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"3l716FhfJUS0kUI7jW3_eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"133","text":"4. Otras causas\\Nde disfagia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Anillos/webs esofágicos.","guid":"HE--f6GZUGno4EYNwRg3_Q","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"• Peristalsis alterada (trastornos de motilidad esofágica).","guid":"rQf7xwgnY2NhBdNPtNzFew","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"• Disfagia progresiva lenta para sólidos con obstrucción episódica → Estenosis o cáncer esofágico.","guid":"m-HvESOlxnwpNb8JMVD7RQ","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"TI8Z6jpULCkTZoFhqR1AgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"133","text":"5. Odinofagia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Causas: Esófagitis infecciosa o inducida por medicamentos.","guid":"Xl3LetCJJkgd3mgQkPZn_A","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"3aNNkA-4itVZ9WFZf0kmcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"133","text":"6. Hipótesis\\Nde reflujo:","guid":"0ZCU11HEMiL2N3Rra2kAfw","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Hipersensibilidad\\Nal reflujo:","guid":"889qy5YG0xkpk5rieUMRDg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• Exposición ácida normal.","guid":"1cRhAqKVv1qtaxIpDrEN8A","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• Asociación de síntomas positiva con reflujo ácido o débilmente ácido.","guid":"d5K21BVXXKzXwS2dbTNX-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"151","text":"• Pirosis funcional:","guid":"UJzpyOIMushT4q1iTwPBig","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"• Exposición ácida normal.","guid":"C3gyEQSAGPwmcaj4JA1Zow","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"• Asociación de síntomas negativa con reflujo.","guid":"_SUs8G0TPXkYL4m60QcI9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"151","text":"• Dx: Pruebas de pH o pH-impedancia.","guid":"yJ5CA-uc1km6XyDStKWDYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"133","text":"7. Dispepsia\\Nfuncional:","guid":"Cis46jAd8fF9G2DarD904g","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Síntomas principales: Saciedad temprana, plenitud postprandial.","guid":"uAlYLTy4NdNZO2R7BONGdg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Pirosis en un tercio de los casos.","guid":"wrqEeYmMbAz8AvHvkUFkNA","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":161,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Gastroenterología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología","filename":"Esofagitis-2024-1","id":"map_659","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Esofagitis-2024-1"}